The open-concept living, kitchen, and dining areas are bathed in natural light and feature warm hardwood floors. A cozy fireplace adds a touch of character and provides a focal point for the room. Four generous bedrooms offer space and comfort for everyone in the family. The master suite boasts a private ensuite bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower, providing a peaceful retreat at the end of the day.
